high_descs: Turn right and walk to the wall, then turn right and take a couple steps. Turn right again and face the green table.
Pick up the spatula on the table.
Walk around the right side of the table and veer left to the sink.
Wash the spatula in the sink.
Turn around and face the table.
Place the spatula on the table in front of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed spatula on a table.

high_descs: Turn right, take a right at the wall and walk to the green table.
Pick up the spatula on the right side of the table.
Turn around, take a left at the corner of the wall and walk to the sink.
Put the spatula in the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the green table.
Put the rinsed spatula on the green table in front of the green sponge.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed spatula on a table.

high_descs: Walk around the kitchen island to face the middle of it.
Pick up the spatula to the right of the lotion bottle.
Turn around to walk to the sink.
Wash the spatula in the sink, removing it afterwards.
Turn around to face the kitchen island.
Set the spatula down on the kitchen island.
anns.task_desc: Wash a spatula and set it back down on the kitchen island.
